f=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>方法</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>setHours()</strong></code>&nbsp;方法根据本地时间为一个日期对象设置小时数，返回从 1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC 到更新后的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>日期</code></a> 对象实例所表示时间的毫秒数。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/date-sethours.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">dateObj.setHours(<em>hoursValue</em>[, <em>minutesValue</em>[, <em>secondsValue</em>[, <em>msValue</em>]]])\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"versions_prior_to_javascript_1.3","title":"JavaScript 1.3 版本之前","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>dateObj.setHours(<em>hoursValue</em>) </code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"hoursvalue\"><code>hoursValue</code></dt>\n <dd>一个 0 到 23 的整数，表示小时。</dd>\n <dt id=\"minutesvalue\"><code>minutesValue</code></dt>\n <dd>一个 0 到 59 的整数，表示分钟。</dd>\n <dt id=\"secondsvalue\"><code>secondsValue</code></dt>\n <dd>一个 0 到 59 的整数，表示秒数。如果指定了&nbsp;<code>secondsValue</code> 参数，则必须同时指定&nbsp;<code>minutesValue&nbsp;</code>参数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"msvalue\"><code>msValue</code></dt>\n <dd>一个 0 到 999 的数字，表示微秒数，如果指定了&nbsp;<code>msValue</code> 参数，则必须同时指定&nbsp;<code>minutesValue</code> 和&nbsp;<code>secondsValue</code>&nbsp;参数。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如果不指定&nbsp;<code>minutesValue</code>，<code>secondsValue</code>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<code>msValue</code> 参数，则会使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMinutes\"><code>getMinutes()</code></a>，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getSeconds\"><code>getSeconds()</code></a> 和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getMilliseconds\"><code>getMilliseconds()</code></a> 方法的返回值。</p>\n\n<p>如果有一个参数超出了合理范围，<code>setHours</code> 会相应地更新日期对象中的日期信息。例如，如果为&nbsp;<code>secondsValue</code>&nbsp;指定了 100，则分钟会加 1，然后秒数使用 40。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example:_using_sethours","title":"例子：使用 <code>setHours</code> 方法","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> theBigDay <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ntheBigDay<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setHours</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"例子：使用 setHours 方法"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范版本</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注解</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ECMAScript 1st Edition. Implemented in JavaScript 1.0</td>\n   <td>Standard</td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.9.5.34\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setHours</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-date.prototype.sethours\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">Date.prototype.setHours</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Date.setHours","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setHours/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/getHours\"><code>Date.prototype.getHours()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setUTCHours\"><code>Date.prototype.setUTCHours()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"描述","id":"description"},{"text":"例子","id":"examples"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"setHours() 方法根据本地时间为一个日期对象设置小时数，返回从 1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC 到更新后的 日期 对象实例所表示时间的毫秒数。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Date.prototype.setHours()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setHours()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setHours()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setHours()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setHours()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Date.prototype.setHours()","loc